大小周也成了行业标配。 “996”模式从互联网公司不成文的潜规则变为明文的企业制度后，还呈现出从互联网行业向传统行业扩散的态势。在所谓的加班文化下，加班往往跟上进联系在一起，员工不加班的下场可能是被“优化”，“被自愿加班”现象则屡见不鲜。 到了今天，整个社会对“996”代表的加班文化的反思越来越多：从“下班后的工作消息要不要回”的讨论，到对“内卷”的批判；从“互联网民工”的自黑，到“打工人”的自嘲。这次，两部门明确指出“996工作制”违法之所以引发巨大反响，就在于跟社会情绪“接驳”。这会倒逼更多互联网企业正视畸形加班文化的弊端，及时转变用工思路。“996”是互联网行业用工史上的一段弯路--经济·科技--人民网"},"attached_info":"ClQInveSkaLDi7AuEAMaCDcwMjEwMTI2IKfV5YkGMAQ4UEAmcgk0ODU2Nzc1MTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I=","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-31a092e05a2f366c2bbee244715902cf_720w.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"39_1631243269.5821092","card_id":"Q_462080546","target":{"id":462080546,"title":"吸尘器到底买哪个牌子的好？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/462080546","type":"question","created":1622289744,"answer_count":32,"follower_count":70,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[307,1309,3519,52320,213653],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"家里有狗，最好尘盒滤芯可以水洗，收纳墙上不用打洞。大家推荐一下"},"attached_info":"Cj4InveSkaLDi7AuEAMaCDY0OTY0MDE5INDayIUGMAE4RkAncgk0NjIwODA1NDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-5b814b34fc2b1afae1c8651b1b312f3d_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"40_1631243269.5825746","card_id":"Q_484334953","target":{"id":484334953,"title":"20岁了，觉得自己很迷茫，总感觉还像个孩子一样找不到方向怎么办?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/484334953","type":"question","created":1630596868,"answer_count":166,"follower_count":285,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[28967,167979,195097],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt"